CMorseRunner Licensing Notice
=============================

This repository contains files under more than one license.

Background
----------

CMorseRunner is a C++/Qt6 port of MorseRunner by Alex Shovkoplyas VE3NEA:
https://www.dxatlas.com/MorseRunner/

Parts of this repository adapt non-trivial logic, algorithms, constants,
and state-machine behavior from the original Delphi/Pascal implementation.
Those original source files were distributed under the Mozilla Public
License 2.0 with the "Incompatible With Secondary Licenses" notice.

Because of that, the adapted files in this repository are not offered as
GPL-2.0-only.

License Allocation
------------------

The following files and directories are distributed under MPL-2.0:

- src/audio/**
- src/core/**

These files contain adapted logic from the original MorseRunner source.

The following files are distributed under GPL-2.0-only:

- .gitignore
- CMakeLists.txt
- README.md
- src/main.cpp
- src/ui/**

These files were written for this port and are offered under GPL-2.0-only
by Izumi Chino <BI6DX>.

Combined Distribution
---------------------

The repository as a whole is a collection of MPL-2.0 files and
GPL-2.0-only files. It should not be described as being available under
GPL-2.0-only as a single work.

No statement in this repository should be read as relicensing any
MPL-2.0-covered file under GPL-2.0-only.

If you modify or redistribute files under src/audio or src/core, comply
with MPL-2.0 for those files.

If you modify or redistribute the GPL-2.0-only files listed above,
comply with GPL-2.0-only for those files.

When redistributing this repository, preserve this notice and both full
license texts.

